{"tid":1201430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（出發前必睇）Netflix 紀錄片 Winter On Fire - 烏克蘭人2014年如何由學生運動至走向獨立","createTime":"2019-06-11T04:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:44:49.000Z","uid":20689,"like":147,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"87cd297070af56f3caae8ab7967664b59fc7df32","tid":1201430,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTY4MDgwOTI3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxMjU3NjE@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BNTY4MDgwOTI3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxMjU3NjE%40._V1_.jpg&h=3cd7b9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/80031666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Fhk%2Ftitle%2F80031666&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=f62cf222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/80031666</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">\nHKG財經台Gdrive 下載 (內含高登中文字幕):\nhttps://drive.google.com/open?id=0Bwb5J1CwZ5KVZ1p1RkFUZVZEdEU\n\n更新中文字幕\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/0B5cYR0h_uLP7b2pieWJybUtyc3M/view</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（各位出發前一定要必睇）</span></span><br />\n凜冬烈火：烏克蘭自由之戰- Netflix 紀念片講2013烏克蘭獨立之路 <br />\n<br />\n入面情況同香港好似 又係由學生搞起運動，之後警察先使用武力打到學生見血，逼到民眾出黎<br />\n<br />\n之後有班垃圾扮反對派 之後出黎叫人翻屋企，結果佢地比民眾唾棄 <br />\n<br />\n之後警方武力升級 好多民眾都唔信警察會自己人打自己人，仲大叫「大家也是烏克籣人」（真係好似香港）<br />\n<br />\n之後好多人比警察打傷 運動膠著 民眾無左方向 直到⋯⋯⋯⋯唔劇透 大家自己睇<br />\n<br />\n佢同香港2014真係好似 香港就係差左少少野就可能變成烏克蘭咁⋯<br />\n<br />\n--------------- 劇情分析 -------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=106&amp;v=NWpp9cdN7_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D106%26v%3DNWpp9cdN7_0&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=6747c53e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=106&amp;v=NWpp9cdN7_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2898476/org/bd7c6ea284a9228e131d1410665aff90.png/qU9TZ4qF4WxmNRldcZNl9apNQaVSAvs2eYUAWnmFAFo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2898476%2Forg%2Fbd7c6ea284a9228e131d1410665aff90.png%2FqU9TZ4qF4WxmNRldcZNl9apNQaVSAvs2eYUAWnmFAFo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=36bb1b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大量敲擊，平民樂手 現場有敲擊樂節奏打拍子既重要性<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">\n失去人性的警察，永遠比示威者暴力\n\n在民聚的抗爭行動之中，對立的一定不是高床軟枕的官員，而是警隊。在影片中的別爾庫特部隊，配備精良而且訓練有素，示威者除了人數之外，根本無法有任何優勢。許多人看電視報導烏克蘭示威，或者會覺得示威者很暴力，但我們從影片看到，事實上有著全幅武裝、手持槍械，而且依附著扭曲的「維持社會治安」心態、得到行使暴力不用負責任的「權力」、到後期甚至可以殺人的警察，其衍生出來的行為只會更加扭曲及暴力。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JpkFtEy39UEqqhezojV_UQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njk0O2g9Mzg3O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/Unwire.hk/2016-02-12-16_11_45-694x387.png.cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJpkFtEy39UEqqhezojV_UQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njk0O2g9Mzg3O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2FUnwire.hk%2F2016-02-12-16_11_45-694x387.png.cf.jpg&h=b0917258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲警察對付示威者的心態顯然易見，恨之入骨、不會留情。這也引來民眾的暴力反彈，雙方暴力不斷升級。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">政府無所不用其技，比黑社會還要黑\n\n當極權政府要解散示威時，總是無所不用其技，而且只會比黑社會更加殘酷不仁。在影片中就描述了政府曾派人滲透進示威者之中，並裝成激進派進行衝擊，以求讓警隊進行一個正當的反彈 (後期真的演變成暴力抗爭就不需要了)。除了警隊之外，更僱用了提圖胥基，他們是收錢而唯命是從的傭兵，很多也是罪犯，而且可以進行警隊無法執行的任務，包括火燒有作為醫療站的基地。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部分內容轉至&quot;我續 Netflix，因為一套 Winter on Fire 的烏克蘭自由之戰紀錄片&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/我續-netflix-因為-套-winter-fire-的烏克蘭自由之戰紀錄片-021513956.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%88%91%E7%BA%8C-netflix-%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA-%E5%A5%97-winter-fire-%E7%9A%84%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87-021513956.html&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=a162fbb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/我續-netflix-因為-套-winter-fire-的烏克蘭自由之戰紀錄片-021513956.html</a>"},{"pid":"a7d26af206d03a698b706f55dda9acd851b075cf","tid":1201430,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ced10f80d2a0a166a8b82a99eaedcdf89e96499","tid":1201430,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3cb07d723673da7aa98d3fb48e0ffdb3a145b2","tid":1201430,"uid":146119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc16f6a87b55e501f8d944d925277015b391784","tid":1201430,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"聽日嘉年華帶鼓？"},{"pid":"f58eefbddef1619072f3291371b01dc2324ae026","tid":1201430,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5079fe4948b70d1e965ff86d8d7de9bfe907170d","tid":1201430,"uid":80416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3dc16f6a87b55e501f8d944d925277015b391784","tid":1201430,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"聽日嘉年華帶鼓？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"各施其職"},{"pid":"18e0faf1f28a27f934ecede4ba01b213adeddb2f","tid":1201430,"uid":146119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e08f1646ed0001628fac8da49a8b