學排陣 (34:55)&nbsp;<br />\n有人整左一批木盾(35:15)&nbsp;<br />\n中段左右好多人成功搶警察長鐵盾(45:50)&nbsp;<br />\n經訓練後由以前既散兵遊勇變成方陣<br />\n<br />\n第八：示威法過左之後，開始使用汽油彈同投擲硬物 (44:35)&nbsp;<br />\n之前成功用滅火筒噴退攔路左膠 (44:12)&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n第九：烏克蘭勇武派早中期冇特定形象領袖<br />\n<br />\n第十：第一位犧牲者年僅20（唔好死）<br />\n<br />\n第十一：烏克蘭廣場既地形係平地，但係後段警察已經有Sniper係大廈<br />\n<br />\n第十二：一位唔衝既小朋友參與調酒(47:10)&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n第十三：黑社會藍屍(1:04:05)&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n第十四：差佬已經癡左線，射醫護人士(51:30)，自己擲燃燒彈(1:08:55)<br />\n<br />\n重點係你以為戰鬥民族好威威，其實同你我經歷過既都冇大分別，點解咁快放棄<br />\n人地本身已有民主，都係打生打死先得到自由！！"},{"pid":"c535cbd8298de1463dab45aabccfc0736c34b6f5","tid":1201430,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:35:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫樓主補個ThisAVlink</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thisav.com/playvideo.php?videoid=425425&amp;page=%E5%87%9C%E5%86%AC%E7%83%88%E7%81%AB%EF%BC%9A%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thisav.com%2Fplayvideo.php%3Fvideoid%3D425425%26page%3D%25E5%2587%259C%25E5%2586%25AC%25E7%2583%2588%25E7%2581%25AB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2583%258F%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%2598%25AD%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2588%25B0.html&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=1539489a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thisav.com/playvideo.php?videoid=425425&amp;page=%E5%87%9C%E5%86%AC%E7%83%88%E7%81%AB%EF%BC%9A%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff59e0400d53d4419e7d1f68eef793235b122e7f","tid":1201430,"uid":33495,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"440a3b1b3b5e35586e134934bec97fa09f52570c","tid":1201430,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭同共產黨軍力比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:35:46.000Z","msg":"當時烏克蘭政府背後係普京<br />